import {Router, Switch, Redirect} from 'react-router-dom'

import MainHeader from './components/layout/MainHeader';
import GreatQoutes from './pages/GreatQoutes'
import AddQoute from './pages/AddQoute'
import QouteDetails from './pages/QouteDetails'


function App() {
  return (


      <Switch>
        <Router path='/'>
          <Redirect to='GreatQoutes'/>          
        </Router>

        <Router path='/GreatQoutes' exact>
          <GreatQoutes/>          
        </Router>

        <Router path='/GreatQoutes/:QouteId' exact>
          <QouteDetails/>          
        </Router>

        <Router path='/AddQoute' exact>
          <AddQoute/>
        </Router>
      </Switch>

  );
}

export default App;
